 <i>and makes a pass</i>
 <i>to the back.</i>

00:07:19.439 --> 00:07:20.608 position:19% line:89% align:start
 <i>Now Jito has the ball</i>

00:07:20.641 --> 00:07:22.610 position:16% line:83% align:start
- <i>and he's totally open.</i>
-[pants]

00:07:22.643 --> 00:07:23.978 position:30% line:83% align:start
Don't you guys
get it by now?

00:07:24.011 --> 00:07:27.615 position:13% line:83% align:start
It doesn't matter how much
you try to mark me.

00:07:27.648 --> 00:07:28.916 position:24% line:83% align:start
-You just can't...
-[panting]

00:07:28.950 --> 00:07:30.618 position:38% line:83% align:start
-stop me!
-[grunt]

00:07:30.651 --> 00:07:31.852 position:38% line:83% align:start
-[scream]
-[grunt]

00:07:31.886 --> 00:07:33.220 position:44% line:83% align:start
[ann]
 <i>Jito now kicks the ball</i>

00:07:33.254 --> 00:07:34.422 position:19% line:89% align:start
 <i>from the penalty area</i>

00:07:34.454 --> 00:07:36.590 position:27% line:83% align:start
 <i>directly towards</i>
 <i>the opponent's goal.</i>

00:07:37.625 --> 00:07:39.427 position:24% line:83% align:start
 <i>The ball's headed</i>
 <i>straight for the keeper.</i>

00:07:39.459 --> 00:07:41.662 position:35% line:89% align:start
[grunting]

00:07:41.696 --> 00:07:43.463 position:16% line:83% align:start
[ann] <i>And Team Nankatsu's</i>
 <i>goalkeeper</i>

00:07:43.496 --> 00:07:44.665 position:27% line:83% align:start
 <i>catches the ball</i>
 <i>with his hands.</i>

00:07:44.699 --> 00:07:46.901 position:19% line:89% align:start
You got this, Morisaki!

00:07:46.934 --> 00:07:53.574 position:35% line:89% align:start
[groaning]

00:07:53.607 --> 00:07:56.310 position:16% line:83% align:start
[ann] <i>The sheer raw power</i>
 <i>from the shot</i>

00:07:56.344 --> 00:07:57.578 position:13% line:83% align:start
- <i>made the ball go in along</i>
-[grunt]

00:07:57.611 --> 00:07:58.980 position:19% line:83% align:start
- <i>with the goalkeeper.</i>
-This can't be happening!

00:07:59.013 --> 00:07:59.680 position:38% line:89% align:start
Morisaki!

00:08:00.614 --> 00:08:02.817 position:27% line:83% align:start
[ann] <i>This is...</i>
 <i>This is incredible!</i>

00:08:02.850 --> 00:08:05.553 position:19% line:83% align:start
 <i>Team Hirado is leading</i>
 <i>the scoreboard already.</i>

00:08:05.586 --> 00:08:08.823 position:10% line:83% align:start
 <i>They're ahead by a two goal</i>
 <i>margin to nothing.</i>

00:08:08.856 --> 00:08:10.591 position:35% line:89% align:start
[cheering]

00:08:10.624 --> 00:08:12.927 position:27% line:83% align:start
[ann] <i>Even though</i>
 <i>it's their first time here,</i>

00:08:12.960 --> 00:08:15.696 position:19% line:83% align:start
 <i>Team Hirado has shown</i>
 <i>to be a strong team</i>

00:08:15.730 --> 00:08:17.098 position:21% line:89% align:start
 <i>in this tournament.</i>

00:08:17.131 --> 00:08:19.834 position:19% line:83% align:start
 <i>This is the first time</i>
 <i>Team Nankatsu's in danger</i>

00:08:19.867 --> 00:08:21.635 position:35% line:83% align:start
 <i>of losing</i>
 <i>the quarterfinals.</i>

00:08:21.669 --> 00:08:24.438 position:16% line:83% align:start
 <i>No one saw this coming,</i>
 <i>ladies and gentlemen.</i>

00:08:24.472 --> 00:08:25.573 position:16% line:89% align:start
 <i>Could this be the end of</i>

00:08:25.606 --> 00:08:27.441 position:27% line:83% align:start
 <i>Team Nankatsu's</i>
 <i>winning streak?</i>

00:08:27.475 --> 00:08:28.542 position:35% line:89% align:start
Nankatsu...

00:08:28.576 --> 00:08:30.578 position:19% line:83% align:start
-is in serious danger.
-Huh?

00:08:31.412 --> 00:08:32.747 position:27% line:83% align:start
[ann] <i>Both goals</i>
 <i>were possible</i>

00:08:32.780 --> 00:08:35.616 position:16% line:83% align:start
 <i>because of Team Hirado's</i>
 <i>powerful duo, Jito and Sano,</i>

00:08:35.649 --> 00:08:37.418 position:27% line:83% align:start
 <i>in a potent and</i>
 <i>dangerous combination.</i>

00:08:37.451 --> 00:08:38.919 position:27% line:83% align:start
 <i>We're witnessing</i>
 <i>something unreal.</i>

00:08:38.953 --> 00:08:41.088 position:19% line:83% align:start
 <i>Team Hirado's captain</i>
 <i>has more strength</i>

00:08:41.122 --> 00:08:42.189 position:19% line:89% align:start
 <i>than any player here.</i>

00:08:42.223 --> 00:08:44.959 position:21% line:83% align:start
 <i>He's Team Nankatsu's</i>
 <i>biggest problem thus far.</i>

00:08:44.992 --> 00:08:47.795 position:24% line:83% align:start
 <i>Captain Tsubasa is</i>
 <i>completely speechless.</i>

00:08:47.828 --> 00:08:48.896 position:41% line:89% align:start
[growl]

00:08:48.929 --> 00:08:51.232 position:16% line:83% align:start
[ann] <i>Team Hirado turned</i>
 <i>out to be a dark horse.</i>

00:08:51.265 --> 00:08:53.667 position:21% line:83% align:start
 <i>Their determination</i>
 <i>has surprised all of us.</i>

00:08:53.701 --> 00:08:55.403 position:21% line:83% align:start
How do you like that,
Nankatsu?

00:08:55.436 --> 00:08:56.804 position:33% line:83% align:start
You won't win
this tournament.

00:08:57.772 --> 00:08:59.940 position:27% line:83% align:start
Seems like Hirado
is an unpredictable team.

00:08:59.974 --> 00:09:01.208 position:30% line:89% align:start
Unpredictable?

00:09:01.242 --> 00:09:02.309 position:19% line:89% align:start
They appear to be weak,

00:09:02.343 --> 00:09:03.911 position:35% line:83% align:start
but they're
a very strong team.

00:09:04.845 --> 00:09:07.648 position:30% line:83% align:start
In the Nagasaki
regional tournament...

00:09:07.681 --> 00:09:10.551 position:21% line:83% align:start
everyone thought that
Team Saikai would win,

00:09:10.584 --> 00:09:12.286 position:30% line:83% align:start
but in the end,
Hirado beat them

00:09:12.319 --> 00:09:13.721 position:27% line:89% align:start
six goals to nil.

00:09:13.754 --> 00:09:16.357 position:30% line:83% align:start
They're a team
that truly relishes...

00:09:16.390 --> 00:09:19.693 position:13% line:83% align:start
in the element of surprise
in soccer.

00:09:19.727 --> 00:09:21.896 position:24% line:83% align:start
So that means that
their strength is the same.

00:09:21.929 --> 00:09:23.030 position:27% line:83% align:start
They play calmly
and they keep

00:09:23.064 --> 00:09:24.765 position:24% line:83% align:start
their cards hidden
until the end.

00:09:24.799 --> 00:09:26.434 position:16% line:89% align:start
No, that's not always it.

00:09:26.467 --> 00:09:27.835 position:33% line:83% align:start
I'd say that
their style of play is

00:09:27.868 --> 00:09:29.870 position:16% line:83% align:start
adapting to the opposing
team's strength.

00:09:29.904 --> 00:09:30.638 position:44% line:89% align:start
What?

00:09:30.671 --> 00:09:32.206 position:30% line:83% align:start
However strong
their rival is,

00:09:32.239 --> 00:09:35.510 position:19% line:83% align:start
that's how strong they
become when they're playing.

00:09:35.544 --> 00:09:36.777 position:27% line:89% align:start
Jito's like that.

00:09:36.811 --> 00:09:38.547 position:33% line:83% align:start
The stronger
his opponent is,

00:09:38.579 --> 00:09:41.615 position:24% line:83% align:start
the more his desire
to surpass and beat him is.

00:09:41.649 --> 00:09:43.918 position:21% line:83% align:start
Tell me, what's wrong
with you, Nankatsu?

00:09:43.951 --> 00:09:45.820 position:27% line:83% align:start
If you guys don't
try to stop us,

00:09:45.853 --> 00:09:47.522 position:16% line:89% align:start
this won't be fun at all.

00:09:47.556 --> 00:09:48.589 position:44% line:89% align:start
What?

00:09:48.622 --> 00:09:50.624 position:24% line:83% align:start
We had our hopes up
when we found out

00:09:50.658 --> 00:09:52.059 position:21% line:83% align:start
we'd be playing you,
Tsubasa.

00:09:52.093 --> 00:09:53.961 position:24% line:83% align:start
But I noticed that
the teams you defeated

00:09:53.994 --> 00:09:56.097 position:35% line:83% align:start
were trash,
just like you are.

00:09:56.130 --> 00:09:59.133 position:41% line:89% align:start
[laugh]

00:09:59.166 --> 00:10:00.367 position:21% line:89% align:start
You should get ready.

00:10:00.401 --> 00:10:01.936 position:35% line:83% align:start
This time,
I'll score on you.

00:10:01.969 --> 00:10:04.972 position:13% line:83% align:start
[narr] <i>We'll be right back</i>
 <i>with Captain Tsubasa.</i>

00:10:08.676 --> 00:10:09.877 position:41% line:83% align:start
[narr]
 <i>And we're back.</i>

00:10:11.011 --> 00:10:13.747 position:21% line:83% align:start
[ann] <i>Team Hirado is</i>
 <i>playing impressively well.</i>

00:10:13.781 --> 00:10:16.317 position:24% line:83% align:start
 <i>Now Team Nankatsu</i>
 <i>has to score two goals</i>

00:10:16.350 --> 00:10:17.685 position:24% line:89% align:start
 <i>to tie the match.</i>

00:10:17.718 --> 00:10:20.589 position:16% line:83% align:start
 <i>That is if they want to</i>
 <i>make a comeback.</i>

00:10:20.621 --> 00:10:22.490 position:10% line:89% align:start
We have to support our team.

00:10:22.524 --> 00:10:24.258 position:16% line:89% align:start
Nankatsu, let's win this!

00:10:24.291 --> 00:10:25.159 position:27% line:83% align:start
-Let's win this!
-Let's win this!

00:10:25.192 --> 00:10:27.027 position:19% line:83% align:start
You can't lose to them,
you hear me?

00:10:27.061 --> 00:10:30.631 position:24% line:83% align:start
You can still turn
this thing around, Nankatsu.

00:10:30.664 --> 00:10:31.799 position:41% line:89% align:start
 <i>Right.</i>

00:10:31.832 --> 00:10:32.867 position:21% line:89% align:start
 <i>It is not over yet.</i>

00:10:33.701 --> 00:10:35.870 position:38% line:83% align:start
 <i>I swear,</i>
 <i>I'll score this time.</i>

00:10:35.903 --> 00:10:36.770 position:38% line:89% align:start
[whistle]

00:10:36.804 --> 00:10:38.439 position:24% line:89% align:start
Come with me, guys.

00:10:38.472 --> 00:10:38.939 position:41% line:83% align:start
-Yeah!
-Yeah!

00:10:39.807 --> 00:10:41.108 position:24% line:83% align:start
[ann] <i>It looks like</i>
 <i>Team Hirado</i>

00:10:41.142 --> 00:10:43.811 position:19% line:83% align:start
 <i>will spend their time</i>
 <i>defending until half time.</i>

00:10:43.844 --> 00:10:44.845 position:19% line:89% align:start
Just like I thought...

00:10:44.879 --> 00:10:47.047 position:19% line:83% align:start
-Now they're defending.
-Huh?

00:10:47.081 --> 00:10:48.916 position:21% line:83% align:start
Team Hirado is famous
for their defense.

00:10:48.949 --> 00:10:50.985 position:27% line:83% align:start
No one has scored
a goal on them until now.

00:10:51.018 --> 00:10:52.786 position:13% line:83% align:start
They want to take advantage
of their lead

00:10:52.820 --> 00:10:55.122 position:21% line:83% align:start
and defend to secure
their victory.

00:10:55.156 --> 00:10:56.423 position:24% line:89% align:start
They don't plan...

00:10:56.457 --> 00:10:58.159 position:16% line:89% align:start
to leave this up to luck.

00:10:58.192 --> 00:10:59.927 position:44% line:83% align:start
Yeah!
It's my turn.

00:10:59.960 --> 00:11:01.530 position:44% line:83% align:start
-Huh?
-[Hajime] [groan]

00:11:01.563 --> 00:11:02.531 position:44% line:83% align:start
[ann]
 <i>What's this?</i>

00:11:02.564 --> 00:11:04.633 position:27% line:83% align:start
 <i>Taki and Kisugi</i>
 <i>aren't moving.</i>

00:11:04.665 --> 00:11:05.799 position:38% line:83% align:start
-[groan]
-[ann] <i>It looks like</i>

00:11:05.833 --> 00:11:07.636 position:16% line:83% align:start
 <i>their previous collision</i>
 <i>with Jito</i>

00:11:07.668 --> 00:11:09.937 position:24% line:83% align:start
- <i>was very serious.</i>
-Oh no, they're both hurt.

00:11:09.970 --> 00:11:10.671 position:41% line:89% align:start
[groan]

00:11:10.704 --> 00:11:12.139 position:33% line:89% align:start
 <i>My shoulder!</i>

00:11:12.173 --> 00:11:13.274 position:35% line:89% align:start
It's time.

00:11:13.307 --> 00:11:14.408 position:35% line:89% align:start
Move, guys.

00:11:14.441 --> 00:11:16.377 position:13% line:89% align:start
I want you to destroy him.

00:11:16.410 --> 00:11:18.045 position:41% line:83% align:start
-Yeah!
-Yeah!

00:11:18.679 --> 00:11:19.713 position:41% line:89% align:start
[grunt]

00:11:19.747 --> 00:11:20.447 position:27% line:89% align:start
You're done for!

00:11:21.616 --> 00:11:23.050 position:21% line:83% align:start
[ann] <i>Captain Tsubasa</i>
 <i>manages to fool</i>

00:11:23.083 --> 00:11:24.451 position:27% line:83% align:start
- <i>the defenders.</i>
-It's yours, Mamoru.

00:11:24.485 --> 00:11:25.719 position:41% line:83% align:start
[grunt]
Here!

00:11:25.753 --> 00:11:27.087 position:27% line:83% align:start
[ann] <i>A beautiful</i>
 <i>one-two pass.</i>

00:11:27.121 --> 00:11:28.889 position:10% line:83% align:start
- <i>Izawa and Tsubasa make way</i>
-[grunt]

00:11:28.923 --> 00:11:29.990 position:13% line:83% align:start
- <i>with excellent maneuvers.</i>
-Mamoru,

00:11:30.024 --> 00:11:31.825 position:19% line:83% align:start
-go to the danger zone.
-Yeah.

00:11:31.859 --> 00:11:33.093 position:44% line:83% align:start
[ann]
 <i>This is the first time</i>

00:11:33.127 --> 00:11:35.530 position:24% line:83% align:start
 <i>we see Tsubasa run</i>
 <i>all the way down the wing.</i>

00:11:35.564 --> 00:11:36.631 position:30% line:89% align:start
Pay attention.

00:11:36.665 --> 00:11:38.365 position:27% line:83% align:start
I want you to get
number 8.

00:11:38.399 --> 00:11:40.201 position:27% line:83% align:start
Let me take care
of the rest.

00:11:40.234 --> 00:11:41.235 position:44% line:89% align:start
Yeah!

00:11:42.236 --> 00:11:42.403 position:44% line:89% align:start
Here!

00:11:43.737 --> 00:11:46.040 position:24% line:83% align:start
[ann] <i>Tsubasa kicks</i>
 <i>a crossover pass to Izawa.</i>

00:11:46.073 --> 00:11:48.275 position:19% line:83% align:start
 <i>Team Nankatsu will try</i>
 <i>to score their first goal</i>

00:11:48.309 --> 00:11:49.376 position:27% line:83% align:start
- <i>with a volley.</i>
-[yell]

00:11:49.410 --> 00:11:50.344 position:41% line:89% align:start
[yell]

00:11:50.377 --> 00:11:52.313 position:30% line:83% align:start
-This can't be!
-Your turn!

00:11:53.682 --> 00:11:55.182 position:44% line:83% align:start
[ann]
 <i>Izawa feints a header,</i>

00:11:55.216 --> 00:11:57.686 position:16% line:83% align:start
 <i>and Nagano goes forward</i>
 <i>to head the ball.</i>

00:11:57.718 --> 00:11:59.153 position:19% line:89% align:start
Yeah, I'm gonna score!

00:11:59.186 --> 00:11:59.621 position:24% line:89% align:start
Not that fast, kid.

00:11:59.654 --> 00:12:01.021 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasp]

00:12:01.055 --> 00:12:03.791 position:19% line:83% align:start
[ann] <i>But Team Hirado's</i>
 <i>captain intercepts the ball,</i>

00:12:03.824 --> 00:12:06.327 position:16% line:83% align:start
 <i>stealing Team Nankatsu's</i>
 <i>opportunity.</i>

00:12:06.360 --> 00:12:07.494 position:38% line:83% align:start
-[grunt]
-[ann] <i>Takeno</i>

00:12:07.529 --> 00:12:08.462 position:24% line:83% align:start
- <i>now has the ball.</i>
-[grunt]

00:12:08.495 --> 00:12:09.698 position:30% line:83% align:start
 <i>And he shoots</i>
 <i>a long pass.</i>

00:12:09.730 --> 00:12:10.731 position:41% line:89% align:start
[grunt]

00:12:10.764 --> 00:12:11.899 position:44% line:83% align:start
[ann]
 <i>Sano receives it.</i>

00:12:12.866 --> 00:12:14.134 position:30% line:83% align:start
Guys, stop him
from shooting.

00:12:14.168 --> 00:12:16.270 position:16% line:83% align:start
-I won't let you through.
-[panting]

00:12:16.303 --> 00:12:17.371 position:41% line:89% align:start
[grunt]

00:12:17.404 --> 00:12:18.305 position:41% line:89% align:start
[grunt]

00:12:18.339 --> 00:12:20.207 position:41% line:83% align:start
-[gasp]
-Ah!

00:12:20.241 --> 00:12:21.375 position:41% line:83% align:start
-[yell]
-[scream]

00:12:21.408 --> 00:12:23.043 position:13% line:89% align:start
Let's make this very clear.

00:12:23.077 --> 00:12:25.680 position:21% line:83% align:start
Nankatsu isn't a team
you can take lightly,

00:12:25.714 --> 00:12:26.615 position:35% line:89% align:start
you punks.

00:12:26.648 --> 00:12:28.215 position:21% line:89% align:start
Great job, Takasugi.

00:12:28.249 --> 00:12:30.851 position:24% line:83% align:start
[ann] <i>Team Nankatsu</i>
 <i>won't concede another goal.</i>

00:12:30.884 --> 00:12:32.753 position:24% line:83% align:start
 <i>Takasugi advances</i>
 <i>with the ball,</i>

00:12:32.786 --> 00:12:34.855 position:21% line:83% align:start
 <i>but Jito gets closer</i>
 <i>to get it back.</i>

00:12:34.888 --> 00:12:37.324 position:19% line:83% align:start
Let's see how you fair
against me, Jito.

00:12:37.358 --> 00:12:38.425 position:41% line:89% align:start
[grunt]

00:12:38.459 --> 00:12:39.860 position:38% line:89% align:start
[grunts]

00:12:39.893 --> 00:12:42.396 position:21% line:83% align:start
[ann] <i>This is a duel</i>
 <i>between titans.</i>

00:12:42.429 --> 00:12:43.130 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:12:43.163 --> 00:12:47.636 position:35% line:89% align:start
[growling]

00:12:47.669 --> 00:12:49.036 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasp]

00:12:49.069 --> 00:12:51.071 position:30% line:83% align:start
[ann] <i>Takasugi</i>
 <i>is knocked down</i>

00:12:51.105 --> 00:12:52.741 position:13% line:83% align:start
- <i>by the superior strength</i>
-[chuckle]

00:12:52.773 --> 00:12:53.675 position:13% line:89% align:start
 <i>of Team Hirado's captain.</i>

00:12:53.708 --> 00:12:55.776 position:38% line:83% align:start
-[grunt]
-What?!

00:12:55.809 --> 00:12:58.513 position:27% line:83% align:start
[ann] <i>But Tsubasa</i>
 <i>steals the ball from Jito</i>

00:12:58.546 --> 00:12:59.780 position:21% line:89% align:start
 <i>for the first time.</i>

00:12:59.813 --> 00:13:02.349 position:21% line:83% align:start
He was able to steal
the ball from the captain!

00:13:02.383 --> 00:13:03.284 position:41% line:89% align:start
[smirk]

00:13:03.752 --> 00:13:04.952 position:30% line:89% align:start
Good, Tsubasa.

00:13:04.985 --> 00:13:06.521 position:13% line:89% align:start
I was getting kinda bored.

00:13:08.723 --> 00:13:09.823 position:38% line:83% align:start
[Hajime]
 <i>Tsubasa is still running</i>

00:13:09.857 --> 00:13:11.358 position:10% line:89% align:start
 <i>despite his shoulder injury.</i>

