00:19:18.126 --> 00:19:19.259 position:27% line:83% align:start
-We're gonna win!
-One more goal.

00:19:19.292 --> 00:19:20.128 position:38% line:83% align:start
-No way!
-Yeah!

00:19:20.160 --> 00:19:21.529 position:10% line:89% align:start
That team is nothing for us.

00:19:21.562 --> 00:19:23.064 position:27% line:83% align:start
We have to score
more goals on them,

00:19:23.097 --> 00:19:24.065 position:24% line:89% align:start
don't we, Captain?

00:19:24.098 --> 00:19:25.733 position:19% line:83% align:start
-No, that'll be enough.
-Huh?

00:19:25.767 --> 00:19:27.969 position:24% line:83% align:start
We're only going to
concentrate on the defense

00:19:28.002 --> 00:19:29.771 position:19% line:89% align:start
during the second half.

00:19:29.804 --> 00:19:30.772 position:44% line:83% align:start
-Huh?
-Huh?

00:19:33.641 --> 00:19:35.143 position:35% line:89% align:start
[groaning]

00:19:35.175 --> 00:19:36.778 position:13% line:89% align:start
I can't even feel my legs.

00:19:36.811 --> 00:19:37.979 position:35% line:89% align:start
[groaning]

00:19:38.012 --> 00:19:38.980 position:35% line:89% align:start
Captain...

00:19:39.013 --> 00:19:40.915 position:13% line:89% align:start
Oh, I didn't see you, Sano.

00:19:40.948 --> 00:19:42.984 position:13% line:89% align:start
The coach keeps insisting.

00:19:43.017 --> 00:19:45.285 position:24% line:83% align:start
He says you should
stay on the team.

00:19:45.318 --> 00:19:46.386 position:16% line:89% align:start
We're really strong when

00:19:46.420 --> 00:19:47.922 position:24% line:83% align:start
we're alongside you
on the pitch.

00:19:47.955 --> 00:19:49.157 position:41% line:89% align:start
Humph.

00:19:49.189 --> 00:19:52.026 position:16% line:83% align:start
Even if I want to leave,
they'll force me to stay.

00:19:52.060 --> 00:19:53.360 position:10% line:89% align:start
But the truth is that soccer

00:19:53.393 --> 00:19:55.429 position:27% line:83% align:start
has never really
interested me.

00:19:55.462 --> 00:19:58.265 position:16% line:83% align:start
Is that why you're always
out picking fights, captain?

00:19:58.298 --> 00:19:59.667 position:19% line:89% align:start
If I'm being honest...

00:20:00.902 --> 00:20:02.269 position:24% line:83% align:start
I'm just trying to
finally find

00:20:02.302 --> 00:20:04.204 position:30% line:83% align:start
someone worthy
of going up against,

00:20:04.237 --> 00:20:08.843 position:21% line:83% align:start
but I'm afraid that's
never going to happen.

00:20:08.876 --> 00:20:09.844 position:27% line:89% align:start
Never say never.

00:20:09.877 --> 00:20:10.343 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:20:11.244 --> 00:20:13.681 position:38% line:83% align:start
[Mitsuru]
Look, he sounds interesting.

00:20:13.715 --> 00:20:16.416 position:24% line:83% align:start
He's the captain of
Team Nankatsu,

00:20:16.450 --> 00:20:17.652 position:19% line:89% align:start
the current champions.

00:20:17.685 --> 00:20:20.655 position:35% line:83% align:start
They've won
the last two tournaments.

00:20:20.688 --> 00:20:21.556 position:33% line:89% align:start
Are you sure?

00:20:21.589 --> 00:20:23.791 position:27% line:83% align:start
Are you sure he's
as strong as they say?

00:20:23.825 --> 00:20:24.892 position:41% line:89% align:start
Uh-huh.

00:20:24.926 --> 00:20:26.426 position:19% line:83% align:start
All of the soccer teams
in Japan

00:20:26.460 --> 00:20:28.930 position:19% line:83% align:start
are training to defeat
Tsubasa Ozora.

00:20:28.963 --> 00:20:30.965 position:16% line:89% align:start
They say he's invincible.

00:20:30.998 --> 00:20:32.432 position:44% line:89% align:start
Oh...

00:20:37.605 --> 00:20:39.941 position:21% line:83% align:start
It looks like I have
no other option.

00:20:39.974 --> 00:20:40.908 position:38% line:83% align:start
[Mitsuru]
Option?

00:20:40.942 --> 00:20:42.677 position:24% line:83% align:start
If I want to fight
against him,

00:20:42.710 --> 00:20:45.546 position:13% line:83% align:start
then I have no other choice
but to stay here, do I?

00:20:45.580 --> 00:20:47.949 position:24% line:83% align:start
I want to face off
against him.

00:20:47.982 --> 00:20:48.950 position:30% line:89% align:start
Yes, Captain...

00:20:49.851 --> 00:20:50.818 position:41% line:83% align:start
Uh-huh.
Yeah!

00:20:52.754 --> 00:20:54.922 position:13% line:83% align:start
[Hiroshi] <i>This whole time,</i>
 <i>I yearned to face off</i>

00:20:54.956 --> 00:20:56.657 position:19% line:89% align:start
 <i>against Team Nankatsu.</i>

00:20:56.691 --> 00:20:59.727 position:24% line:83% align:start
 <i>Especially against</i>
 <i>Tsubasa Ozora.</i>

00:20:59.761 --> 00:21:01.162 position:27% line:83% align:start
 <i>But in the end,</i>
 <i>it was nothing</i>

00:21:01.195 --> 00:21:02.462 position:19% line:89% align:start
 <i>but a disappointment.</i>

00:21:04.431 --> 00:21:06.399 position:30% line:83% align:start
 <i>It looks like</i>
 <i>there's no one worthy</i>

00:21:06.433 --> 00:21:08.368 position:16% line:89% align:start
 <i>of facing head to head.</i>

00:21:08.401 --> 00:21:09.937 position:41% line:83% align:start
[narr]
 <i>Infirmary.</i>

00:21:09.971 --> 00:21:10.972 position:33% line:89% align:start
Three goals.

00:21:11.739 --> 00:21:12.405 position:24% line:89% align:start
You're in a pinch.

00:21:13.406 --> 00:21:15.843 position:21% line:83% align:start
It'll be hard to tie
the score, young man.

00:21:15.877 --> 00:21:17.145 position:41% line:89% align:start
I know.

00:21:17.178 --> 00:21:19.814 position:24% line:83% align:start
But I still haven't
given up yet.

00:21:19.847 --> 00:21:20.815 position:33% line:89% align:start
This time...

00:21:20.848 --> 00:21:22.884 position:30% line:83% align:start
I'll do my best
to shoot my Drive Shot

00:21:22.917 --> 00:21:24.752 position:13% line:89% align:start
to even out the scoreboard.

00:21:25.887 --> 00:21:27.320 position:24% line:89% align:start
This isn't over...

00:21:27.354 --> 00:21:29.624 position:16% line:89% align:start
until it's over, doctor.

00:21:29.657 --> 00:21:30.525 position:38% line:89% align:start
[chuckle]

00:21:30.558 --> 00:21:32.693 position:10% line:83% align:start
-He's going to be just fine.
-[giggles]

00:21:32.727 --> 00:21:35.062 position:33% line:83% align:start
Taki, Kisugi,
you feeling okay?

00:21:35.096 --> 00:21:36.164 position:27% line:89% align:start
We're doing fine.

00:21:36.197 --> 00:21:37.397 position:10% line:89% align:start
Don't worry about us, coach.

00:21:37.430 --> 00:21:39.332 position:27% line:83% align:start
I'm more worried
about Tsubasa.

00:21:39.366 --> 00:21:40.902 position:30% line:89% align:start
[door opening]

00:21:40.935 --> 00:21:42.069 position:44% line:83% align:start
-Huh?
-Huh?

00:21:42.103 --> 00:21:43.470 position:38% line:83% align:start
-Tsubasa!
-Tsubasa!

00:21:43.504 --> 00:21:45.338 position:35% line:83% align:start
Everybody,
this still hasn't

00:21:45.372 --> 00:21:46.674 position:21% line:89% align:start
finished yet, has it?

00:21:47.275 --> 00:21:48.976 position:30% line:83% align:start
-Yes, Tsubasa.
-Ah!

00:21:49.010 --> 00:21:50.044 position:19% line:83% align:start
-That's right, Tsubasa.
-[laugh]

00:21:50.077 --> 00:21:51.378 position:19% line:83% align:start
-We can do this, guys!
-Oh, yes!

00:21:51.411 --> 00:21:52.613 position:24% line:83% align:start
-I'm sure of that!
-We can make a comeback.

00:21:52.647 --> 00:21:53.648 position:21% line:83% align:start
-We can overcome this
-We can find a way

00:21:53.681 --> 00:21:54.916 position:27% line:83% align:start
-together, guys!
-to win this thing.

00:21:54.949 --> 00:21:57.417 position:21% line:83% align:start
-Let's win, Nankatsu!
-I knew you're a winner.

00:21:57.450 --> 00:22:00.621 position:19% line:83% align:start
 <i>Tsubasa's smile always</i>
 <i>motivates the team.</i>

00:22:00.655 --> 00:22:01.622 position:35% line:89% align:start
 <i>However...</i>

00:22:01.656 --> 00:22:04.324 position:19% line:83% align:start
 <i>I'm worried his injury</i>
 <i>might be serious.</i>

00:22:05.760 --> 00:22:08.796 position:16% line:83% align:start
[ann] <i>We're in the second</i>
 <i>half of the match.</i>

00:22:08.830 --> 00:22:11.464 position:21% line:83% align:start
 <i>Despite his injury,</i>
 <i>the captain Tsubasa</i>

00:22:11.498 --> 00:22:14.035 position:27% line:83% align:start
 <i>will be playing</i>
 <i>in this half.</i>

00:22:14.068 --> 00:22:15.670 position:41% line:89% align:start
[yawn]

00:22:15.703 --> 00:22:17.738 position:16% line:83% align:start
When I say so, I want you
to pass me the ball.

00:22:17.772 --> 00:22:18.773 position:44% line:89% align:start
What?

00:22:18.806 --> 00:22:21.843 position:16% line:83% align:start
I'll score the first goal
for our team, Mamoru.

00:22:21.876 --> 00:22:23.611 position:38% line:89% align:start
[whistle]

00:22:25.279 --> 00:22:27.447 position:21% line:83% align:start
 <i>I hope you're ready,</i>
 <i>Team Hirado.</i>

00:22:27.480 --> 00:22:28.850 position:21% line:89% align:start
 <i>Because this time...</i>

00:22:29.684 --> 00:22:31.953 position:27% line:83% align:start
 <i>I will be using</i>
 <i>my Drive Shot.</i>

00:22:31.986 --> 00:22:33.955 position:27% line:89% align:start
 <i>And we will win!</i>

